### Test Leaderboard API

### 1. Get Leaderboard (default - by total solved)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard?page=0&size=10

### 2. Get Leaderboard sorted by experience
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard?page=0&size=10&sortBy=experience

### 3. Get Leaderboard sorted by level
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard?page=0&size=10&sortBy=level

### 4. Get Leaderboard sorted by current streak
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard?page=0&size=10&sortBy=currentStreak

### 5. Search users by username
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard?search=test&page=0&size=10

### 6. Get Top 5 users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard/top/5

### 7. Get Top 10 users by experience
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard/top/10?sortBy=experience

### 8. Get specific user ranking (replace with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard/user/1/ranking

### 9. Get specific user ranking (test user)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leaderboard/user/2/ranking